                                        <span style="color: black !important;"><p>Cl, Br, I এর&nbsp;d&nbsp;অরবিটাল থাকে কিন্তু&nbsp;F এ&nbsp;d&nbsp;অরবিটাল থাকে না।&nbsp;</p>

clip: rect(3.169em, 1000.67em, 4.137em, -999.998em); top: -3.985em; left: 0em;"><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-309" style="font-family: MathJax_Main;">C</span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px;                                         <span style="color: black !important; font-weight: bold;">Solution:</span>
                                        <br>
                                        <span style="color: black !important;"><p><span class="math-tex"><span class="MathJax_Preview" style="color: inherit; display: none;"></span><span class="MathJax" id="MathJax-Element-43-Frame" tabindex="0" style="position: relative;" data-mathml="<math xmlns=&quot;http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML&quot;><mi>l</mi><mi>p</mi><mo>=</mo><mi>H</mi><mo>.</mo><mi>O</mi><mo>.</mo><mi>N</mi><mo>&amp;#x2212;</mo></math>" role="presentation"><nobr aria-hidden="true"><span class="math" id="MathJax-Span-373" style="width: 6.355em; display: inline-block;"><span style="display: inline-block; position: relative; width: 5.207em; height: 0px; font-size: 122%;"><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(1.15em, 1005.12em, 2.297em, -999.998em); top: -1.965em; left: 0em;"><span class="mrow" id="MathJax-Span-374"><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-375" style="font-family: MathJax_Math-italic;">l</span><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-376" style="font-family: MathJax_Math-italic;">p</span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-377" style="font-family: MathJax_Main;                                     <div class="row solveText" style="display: block; padding:10px; color:#077307; overflow-x: auto; background-color: #d7f7d4;">
                                        <span style="color: black !important; font-weight: bold;">Solution:</span>
                                        <br>
                                        <span style="color: black !important;"><p>অ্যানায়নের আকার বৃদ্ধি পেলে সমযোজী বৈশিষ্ট্য অর্থাৎ দ্রবণীয়তা হ্রাস পেতে থাকে।</p>

                                        <div class="serial"><span>Question 38</span></div>
                                        <div class="questionText" style="display: block;">
                                            <p>নিচের কোন অ্যানায়নের পোলারায়ন ক্ষমতা সর্বনিম্ন?</p>

padding-left: 0.166em;">(</span><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-3030" style="font-family: MathJax_Math-italic;">i</span><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-3031" style="font-family: MathJax_Math-italic;">i</span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-3032" style="font-family: MathJax_Main;">)</span></span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 1.969em;"></span></span></span><span style="display: inline-block; overflow: hidden; vertical-align: -0.348em; border-left: 0px solid; width: 0px; height: 1.302em;"></span></span></nobr><span class="MJX_Assistive_MathML" role="presentation"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><mn>2</mn><mi>y</mi><mo>−</mo><mi>x</mi><mo>−</mo><mn>4</mn><mo>=</mo><mn>0</mn><mo>…</mo><mrow><mo>(</mo><mi>i</mi><mo>)</mo></mrow><mo>;</mo><mn>3</mn><mi>x</mi><mo>−</mo><mn>5</mn><mi>y</mi><mo>+</mo><mn>9</mn><mo>=</mo><mn>0</mn><mo>…</mo><mo stretchy="false">(</mo><mi>i</mi><mi>i</mi><mo stretchy="false">)</mo></math></span></span><script type="math/tex" id="MathJax-Element-207">2y-x-4=0\ldots\left(i\right);3x-5y+9=0\ldots(ii)</script></span></p>

<p>Solving (i) &amp; (ii), ছেদবিন্দু&nbsp;<span class="math-tex"><span class="MathJax_Preview" style="color: inherit; display: none;"></span><span class="MathJax" id="MathJax-Element-208-Frame" tabindex="0" style="position: relative;" data-mathml="<math xmlns=&quot;http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML&quot;><mo stretchy=&quot;false&quot;>(</mo><mn>2</mn><mo>,</mo><mn>3</mn><mo stretchy=&quot;false&quot;>)</mo></math>" role="presentation"><nobr aria-hidden="true"><span class="math" id="MathJax-Span-3033" style="width: 2.215em; display: inline-block;"><span style="display: inline-block; position: relative; width: 1.805em; height: 0px; font-size: 122%;"><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(1.109em, 1001.72em, 2.338em, -999.998em); top: -1.965em; left: 0em;"><span class="mrow" id="MathJax-Span-3034"><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-3035" style="font-family: MathJax_Main;">(</span><span class="mn" id="MathJax-Span-3036" style="font-family: MathJax_Main;">2</span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-3037" style="font-family: MathJax_Main;">,</span><span class="mn" id="MathJax-Span-3038" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.166em;">3</span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-3039" style="font-family: MathJax_Main;">)</span></span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 1.969em;"></span></span></span><span style="display: inline-block; overflow: hidden; vertical-align: -0.348em; border-left: 0px solid; width: 0px; height: 1.302em;"></span></span></nobr><span class="MJX_Assistive_MathML" role="presentation"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><mo stretchy="false">(</mo><mn>2</mn><mo>,</mo><mn>3</mn><mo stretchy="false">)</mo></math></span></span><script type="math/tex" id="MathJax-Element-208">(2,3)</script></span></p>

<p><span class="math-tex"><span class="MathJax_Preview" style="color: inherit; display: none;"></span><span class="MathJax" id="MathJax-Element-209-Frame" tabindex="0" style="position: relative;" data-mathml="<math xmlns=&quot;http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML&quot;><mo>&amp;#x2234;</mo></math>" role="presentation"><nobr aria-hidden="true"><span class="math" id="MathJax-Span-3040" style="width: 0.658em; top: -2.17em; left: 0em;"><span class="mrow" id="MathJax-Span-3041"><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-3042" style="font-family: MathJax_AMS;">∴</span></span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 2.174em;"></span></span></span><span style="display: inline-block; overflow: hidden; vertical-align: -0.148em; border-left: 0px solid; width: 0px; height: 0.753em;"></span></span></nobr><span class="MJX_Assistive_MathML" role="presentation"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><mo>∴</mo></math></span></span><script type="math/tex" id="MathJax-Element-209">\therefore</script></span>&nbsp;নির্ণেয় সরলরেখা,&nbsp;<span class="math-tex"><span class="MathJax_Preview" style="color: inherit; display: none;"></span><span class="MathJax" id="MathJax-Element-210-Frame" tabindex="0" style="position: relative;" data-mathml="<math xmlns=&quot;http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML&quot;><mi>y</mi><mo>&amp;#x2212;</mo><mn>3</mn><mo>=</mo><mfrac><mrow><mn>8</mn><mo>&amp;#x2212;</mo><mn>3</mn></mrow><mrow><mn>3</mn><mo>&amp;#x2212;</mo><mn>2</mn></mrow></mfrac><mrow><mo>(</mo><mrow><mi>x</mi><mo>&amp;#x2212;</mo><mn>2</mn></mrow><mo>)</mo></mrow><mo stretchy=&quot;false&quot;>&amp;#x21D2;</mo><mi>y</mi><mo>&amp;#x2212;</mo><mn>3</mn><mo>=</mo><mn>5</mn><mi>x</mi><mo>&amp;#x2212;</mo><mn>10</mn></math>" role="presentation"><nobr aria-hidden="true"><span class="math" id="MathJax-Span-3043" style="width: 16.6em; top: -1.965em; left: 0em;"><span class="mrow" id="MathJax-Span-3044"><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-3045" style="font-family: MathJax_Math-italic;">y<span style="display: inline-block; overflow: hidden; height: 1px; width: 0.002em;"></span></span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-3046" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.207em;">−</span><span class="mn" id="MathJax-Span-3047" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; font-family: MathJax_Main;">−</span><span class="mn" id="MathJax-Span-3053" style="font-size: 70.7%; font-family: MathJax_Main;">3</span></span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 4.018em;"></span></span><span style="position: absolute; <p><span class="math-tex"><span class="MathJax_Preview" style="color: inherit; display: none;"></span><span class="MathJax" id="MathJax-Element-211-Frame" tabindex="0" style="position: relative;" data-mathml="<math xmlns=&quot;http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML&quot;><mo stretchy=&quot;false&quot;>&amp;#x21D2;</mo><mn>5</mn><mi>x</mi><mo>&amp;#x2212;</mo><mi>y</mi><mo>&amp;#x2212;</mo><mn>7</mn><mo>=</mo><mn>0</mn></math>" role="presentation"><nobr aria-hidden="true"><span class="math" id="MathJax-Span-3074" style="width: 7.625em; <div class="row questionBlock">

                            <div class="row question">
                                <div class="col-md-12" style="padding-left:0px; padding-right:0px;">
                                    <div class="row">
                                        <div class="serial"><span>Question 62</span></div>
                                        <div class="questionText" style="display: block;">

                                            <p>নিষ্ক্রিয় গ্যাসের পর সবচেয়ে নিষ্ক্রিয় মৌল হলো নাইট্রোজেন, কারণ-</p>

                                        <div class="serial"><span>Question 78</span></div>
                                        <div class="questionText" style="display: block;">
                                            <p>সংকর অরবিটালের বৈশিষ্ট্য–<br>
(i) প্রতিটি অরবিটালে সর্বাধিক দুটো ইলেকট্রন থাকে<br>
(ii) অরবিটালে ইলেকট্রন দুটির স্পিন বিপরীতমুখী হয়<br>
(iii) এ অরবিটালসমূহ থেকে সৃষ্ট বন্ধন তুলনামূলক দূর্বল হয়<br>
<strong>নিচের কোনটি সঠিক?</strong></p>

                                        </div>

                                            <p>কোন আয়নটির পোলারায়িত হওয়ার প্রবণতা বেশি?</p>

                                        <span style="color: black !important; font-weight: bold;">Solution:</span>

                                        <span style="color: black !important;"><p>অ্যানায়নের আকার বড় হলে পোলারায়ন প্রবণতা বেশি হয়।</p>
